title: Birthday Cake Cookies
directions: Preheat oven to 350° and line two baking sheets with parchment paper.
In a large bowl, combine cake mix and baking powder. Add eggs, butter, and vanilla, then fold in sprinkles. Scoop out dough with a medium cookie scoop and place on a baking sheet, about 1" apart.
Bake until slightly golden, 12 to 13 minutes. Let cool.
